## Comparison with simply-mcp-ts

| Feature | simply-mcp-ts | simply-mcp-py |
|---------|--------------|---------------|
| Decorator API | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ |
| Functional API | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ |
| Interface API | ‚úÖ | üöß (planned) |
| Builder API | ‚úÖ | üöß (future) |
| Stdio Transport | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ |
| HTTP Transport | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ |
| SSE Transport | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ |
| Watch Mode | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ |
| Bundling | ‚úÖ | ‚úÖ |
| Schema Validation | Zod | Pydantic |
| Type System | TypeScript | Python + mypy |

